cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.NE, cs.DS

The paper proposes a deep learning model for predicting network growth based on the topological structure of a graph. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and network science (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the limitations of existing methods that use hand-crafted features (cs.SD) and graph kernels (cs.NE). Finally, the experiments involve analyzing large collections of real-world networks (cs.DS).
